DATA SEGMENT
 N DW 5
 R DW 2
 RESULT DW 0
 DATA ENDS
 ASSUME CS:CODE,DS:DATA
 CODE SEGMENT
 START: MOV AX,DATA
 MOV DS,AX
 MOV AX,N
 MOV BX,R
 CALL NCR
 INT 03H
 NCR PROC
 CMP BX,0H 
 JE RES1 
 CMP BX,AX
 JE RES1 
 CMP BX,01H 
 JE RESN 
 DEC AX 
 CMP BX,AX 
 JE INCR 
 PUSH AX 
 PUSH BX 
 CALL NCR 
 POP BX 
 POP AX
 DEC BX 
 PUSH AX 
 PUSH BX 
 CALL NCR 
 POP BX 
 POP AX
 RET
 RES1: INC RESULT 
 RET 
 INCR: INC RESULT 
 RESN: ADD RESULT,AX 
 RET 
 NCR ENDP
 CODE ENDS
 END START
